{"id":307520,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/bbc-乌鲁木齐一公车起火至少1人死亡/","date":"2013-08-05T08:18:54Z","modified":"2013-08-05T08:18:54Z","title":"BBC | 乌鲁木齐一公车起火至少1人死亡","content":"<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/1375684372_498.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-307521\" alt=\"1375684372_498\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/1375684372_498.jpg\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/1375684372_498.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/1375684372_498-300x178.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/1375684372_498-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>新疆乌鲁木齐星期一（8月5日）中午发生公共汽车起火燃烧事件，造成至少1人死亡。</p>\n<p>新华社报道称，乌鲁木齐一辆公共汽车11时30分许在行驶中突然起火燃烧。</p>\n<p>新华社称，火灾还造成6人受伤。</p>\n<p>新疆政府官员称，初步调查显示事故原因为车辆线路老化造成起火。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18269,8779],"tags":[12410,16602,23520]}